CHAPTER 2
Engineering Philosophy
Instead of increasing engine size:

Distribute work.

Instead of increasing stress:

Distribute stress.

Instead of one actuator:

Multiple synchronized actuators.

Instead of one thermal source:

Distributed heat generation.

Instead of one failure point:

Distributed redundancy.

