Future Development
Potential future research areas include:

Variable-geometry hydraulic actuators.
Adaptive hydraulic manifolds.
Higher-efficiency rotary actuator designs.
Model-predictive control for energy management.
Advanced thermal management using novel materials.
Lightweight modular chassis integration.
