• Electronic inverter
• EM-220 electric traction motor

MECHANICAL CORE
• ITDM-220 Integrated Torque Distribution Module
  (planetary reduction + torque combination)

HYDRAULIC CORE
• IHPM-220 Integrated Hydraulic Power Module
  - Variable hydraulic pump
  - Compact pressure accumulator
